// Build email content based on team member
const teamMember = $json.customField?.team_member || 'Catriona';
const firstName = $json.firstName || '';
const company = $json.companyName || '';
const openingLine = $json.customField?.personalized_opening || '';

const templates = {
  'Catriona': {
    subject: 'QMSR is live: your QMS gaps just became compliance risks',
    body: `${openingLine}

Sunday, February 2, FDA's Quality Management System Regulation officially replaced the Quality System Regulation. If your quality team is asking "what needs to change right now," you're not alone.

The companies that prepared for QMSR in 2025 have compliant systems today. The ones waiting are now facing urgent remediation with FDA inspections looming.

Worth a 30-minute call this week to assess your current QMSR compliance status?

Best regards,
Catriona Boyd
Director, Quality Services
Avania Clinical`
  },
  'Angela': {
    subject: 'QMSR is live—your first 90 days matter',
    body: `${openingLine}

Three days ago, FDA's Quality Management System Regulation officially replaced the Quality System Regulation. After 25 years navigating FDA regulatory transitions, I can tell you: the companies that get this right in the first 90 days avoid the scramble that hits everyone else.

Worth a 30-minute strategy call this week?

Best regards,
Angela Johnson
Global MedTech Executive, Regulatory Affairs
Avania Clinical`
  },
  'Sam': {
    subject: 'Your AI device needs a PCCP—here's why',
    body: `${openingLine}

If your medical device uses machine learning, you've probably heard about PCCP. What you might not realize: PCCP is quickly becoming FDA's litmus test for whether you understand AI device regulation.

Worth a 30-minute conversation to assess your PCCP readiness?

Best regards,
Sam Engelman
Director, Regulatory Affairs
Avania Clinical`
  },
  'Jasmine': {
    subject: 'Strategic CRO partnership vs. transactional project work',
    body: `${openingLine}

Most medtech companies approach CRO relationships transactionally. Then they're surprised when the CRO delivers exactly what was asked for—but the broader business outcomes fall short.

Worth a 30-minute conversation?

Best regards,
Jasmine Saba
SVP, Strategic Relationships
Avania Clinical`
  },
  'Jeannine': {
    subject: 'The medtech CRO built for companies like yours',
    body: `${openingLine}

Quick question: when you need regulatory strategy, clinical trial execution, and quality system support, are you working with three different vendors—or one integrated partner?

Avania is the world's only medtech-exclusive CRO.

Worth a brief conversation?

Best regards,
Jeannine Umpleby
Director, Business Development
Avania Clinical`
  }
};

const template = templates[teamMember] || templates['Catriona'];
const fromEmail = teamMember.toLowerCase().replace(' ', '.') + '@avaniaclinical.com';

return [{
  json: {
    ...$json,
    emailSubject: template.subject,
    emailBody: template.body,
    fromEmail: fromEmail,
    toEmail: $json.email
  }
}];
